  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 5
  Paragraph: 8
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Ch'ang Chi said, "In the way he goes about it, he uses his knowledge to
get at his mind, and uses his mind to get at the constant mind. Why
should things gather around him?"
